; <br />\n<br />\n或者，都係講清楚一D，但大家咪落廢話留言、廢話提議，咪再激我！我而家留醫期間，暫時間內也不能出醫！事源我中風，情況有些地方好，有些地方不好！現在有政府醫院最專業團隊照顧著我，也感謝他們，明天見腦科醫生！在此正式宣佈:炸兩俠退休了！而若果有什麼事情，向大家先講聲「再見」！<br />\nps.入院前已錄了格羅兹尼！<br />\nps,人生無常！面對命運！</blockquote><br />\n佢打定揾人打字?"},{"pid":"aebd703cc7bcad7dc48cb3511d94f1c7af0cdd4e","tid":473313,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:30:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/192158_9bc11dbc7c3c1915d81107023d3d1586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F192158_9bc11dbc7c3c1915d81107023d3d1586.jpg&h=d85ffb1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪阿祖？"},{"pid":"c13986b103f72e0869f5eef58274910dea71b8ea","tid":473313,"uid":46933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f44bd952272750183b695d189ea9e41b0f31fee","tid":473313,"uid":5780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:41:51.000Z","msg":"雲海!!!"},{"pid":"ed3182c2fc59aa2eff698383d12fad325151348f","tid":473313,"uid":70575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眼光狹窄，盲反中共。<br />\n氣度小，中風實屬預料之內</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"e395f769520dbc7d36868b17ce33db3b766f9cc7","tid":473313,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/192158_9bc11dbc7c3c1915d81107023d3d1586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F192158_9bc11dbc7c3c1915d81107023d3d1586.jpg&